<item>
            <title>[LU-19772] build: Improve the detection of o2iblnd path</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19772</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;1) Make the common config/lustre-lnet.m4 do more check for o2iblnd path.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2)&#160; The common config/lustre-lnet.m4&#160; is the unified way to check o2iblnd path on both rhel and debian so remove the duplicated code. as below:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lustre/scripts/dkms.mkconf:
...
flavor=\$(echo \$kernelver | tr &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;-&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;\\n&apos;&lt;/span&gt; | tail -1)
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; grep -F -q &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;.&apos;&lt;/span&gt; &amp;lt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; \$flavor ; then
&#160; &#160; flavor=&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;;
fi
...
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; [ -d /usr/src/ofa_kernel/\${flavor} ]; then
  &#160; OPTS=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\${OPTS} --with-o2ib=/usr/src/ofa_kernel/\${flavor}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
elif [ -d /usr/src/ofa_kernel/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; ]; then
  &#160; OPTS=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;\${OPTS} --with-o2ib=/usr/src/ofa_kernel/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
fi
...&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
